sequenceDiagram
    participant Customer
    participant Merchant
    participant Gateway as Payment Gateway
    participant Acquirer as Acquirer Bank
    participant Network as Card Network
    participant Issuer as Issuing Bank

    Customer->>Merchant: Request refund (order ID)
    Merchant->>Gateway: POST /refunds (original transaction ID, amount)
    Gateway->>Gateway: Validate original transaction exists and was captured
    Gateway->>Gateway: Check refund amount <= captured amount
    Gateway->>Acquirer: Submit credit instruction
    Acquirer->>Network: Route credit transaction
    Network->>Issuer: Credit cardholder account
    Issuer->>Issuer: Post credit to account (3-10 business days)
    Issuer-->>Network: Credit confirmed
    Network-->>Acquirer: Settlement updated
    Acquirer-->>Gateway: Refund processed
    Gateway-->>Merchant: Refund confirmation + refund ID
    Merchant-->>Customer: Refund confirmation email
